%h3
  经营信息
- if company.credit.present?
  - cr = company.credit
  %table.table.table-striped.table-bordered
    %tbody
      - attr_attr = [:main_product, :sales_region, :clients_type, :upstream, :downstream, :opt_stage]
      - attr_attr.each do |item|
        %tr
          %td.span2
            = Credit.human_attribute_name(item) 
          %td.span4
            = cr.send(item)

- else
  该公司的公司信息尚未检索成功
  %span.badge ?

